      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NEXT BLACK JACK (2) comes off an average performance last start when seventh at this track over 510m behind Cody's Star (30.62) in a OPEN. Was a winner prior to that. Has ability and looks hard to stop. GEORGE ALEXIS (8) is progressing well scoring last time out (23.41) at this track and bringing up his 6th career win. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Can make it two on the bounce. WAKA WAKA (1) had a tricky draw last time and although midfield in fourth wasn't far away finishing 5 lengths from the winner (23.93). Form here at the trip sound including three wins. A big run wouldn't surprise. CAN'T TOUCH ME (4) continues to race well and is sure to be competitive again.",
